//! # GPU Compute Framework
//!
//! High-performance GPU compute shader compilation:
//!
//! - **SPIR-V 1.6**: Full Vulkan/OpenCL compute support
//! - **Workgroups**: Automatic sizing and optimization
//! - **Shared Memory**: Efficient intra-workgroup communication
//! - **Atomics**: Full atomic operation support
//! - **Subgroups**: SIMD-within-SIMT operations
//!
//! ## Example
//!
//! ```quanta
//! @compute(workgroup_size = [256, 1, 1])
//! fn vector_add(
//!     @buffer(set = 0, binding = 0, readonly) a: &[f32],
//!     @buffer(set = 0, binding = 1, readonly) b: &[f32],
//!     @buffer(set = 0, binding = 2) result: &mut [f32],
//! ) {
//!     let idx = global_invocation_id().x;
//!     result[idx] = a[idx] + b[idx];
//! }
//! ```

module quantalang::gpu

